Module fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp
Package fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp

Class CurrentAndForecastWeatherResponse.Daily

java.lang.Object
fi.tuni.prog3.weatherapp.CurrentAndForecastWeatherResponse.Daily
Enclosing class:
CurrentAndForecastWeatherResponse
public static class CurrentAndForecastWeatherResponse.Daily extends Object
The `Daily` class represents the daily forecast for the next 8 days. It contains the time of the forecasted data, sunrise time, sunset time, moonrise time, moonset time, moon phase, human-readable description of the weather conditions for the day, temperature, atmospheric pressure, humidity, dew point, wind speed, wind direction, wind gust, weather condition, cloudiness, probability of precipitation, precipitation volume, snow volume, and UV index.
